Family: Diapensiaceae
Plant Name: *Galax aphylla* L.
Coll. by: A. Gholson, Jr. (Handwritten)
Det. by: AKG (Handwritten)
Date: 25 February 1978 (Handwritten)
Location: Picnic Area south of Etowah River, below Allatoona Dam, Near Cartersville, in Bartow Co., Ga. (Handwritten)

Plant No.: 6871 (Handwritten)
